messages.message:
Brian
Can you do me a favor?
I guess that depends. What's that?

Brian
We have 8 mutual friends.  Can you pick one and give them a compliment?  Which one?
Bryan Diaz?
Heather?
lol
I am directing at least 2 people to do this just to see if they can figure it out where it came from on their own. lol people lack personal connection on FB
If it happens at the same time the person receiving it will be amazed and happy.
lol I must be ahead of my time.

Brian
If it happens at the same time the person receiving it will be amazed and happy.
lol I must be ahead of my time.

I understand what you're trying to do. It is a bit superficial here, and most of the connections I have are from people I've met along the way.
I saw most of them and complimented them at the reunion haha

Brian
Along the way?  Superficial maybe.  What more important is what comes next.  That is good.
I've been friending atheists.  Amazing how much people are willing to talk about their ambitions.

Complete stranger.
Superficial?
Only started with a compliment.

not everything is mutually exclusive, but a lot of people spend more time trying to improve their facebook life instead of their own life, actual conversations aside
I respect that
connecting with strangers and friends alike, that is

Brian
I agree.  But getting people talking about their ambitions makes them more likely to achieve them.
I would agree with that. You can't hit a goal that you don't set, and too many become complacent. Myself included.
I've actually reconnected with Chelsea Dishman a bit since the reunion and we've chatted but not really in regards to goals or ambitions

Brian
Yeah she is very social.
I'm heading out of work, we'll chat another time
